zhao.algorithmMagic.algorithm

接口 OperationAlgorithm

  • 所有已知子接口:
    AggregationAlgorithm, ClassificationAlgorithm, DifferenceAlgorithm<value>, DistanceAlgorithm, FeatureExtractionAlgorithm<returnType,paramType>, GeneratingAlgorithm, GeneratingAlgorithm2D, GeneratingAlgorithmMany, WeightAggregation
    所有已知实现类:
    BatchAggregation, BrayCurtisDistance, CanberraDistance, ChebyshevDistance, CosineDistance, DataStandardization, DecisionTree, DiceCoefficient, DictFeatureExtraction, Dijkstra, Dijkstra2D, DirectionalDijkstra2D, DistanceClassification, EditDistance, EuclideanMetric, ExtremumAggregation, HammingDistance, HausdorffDistance, JaccardSimilarityCoefficient, KMeans, KnnClassification, LinearNormalization, LinearRegression, ManhattanDistance, MinkowskiDistance, ModelAlgorithm, ModularOperation, MultipleLinearRegression, NaiveBayes, OperationAlgorithmManager, ProbabilisticAlgorithm, RandomForest, SchemeAlgorithm, StandardizedEuclideanDistance, StringArrayFeature, UDFDistanceClassification, WeightBatchAggregation, WeightedAverage, WordFrequency, Z_ScoreNormalization, ZhaoCoordinateNet, ZhaoCoordinateNet2D

    public interface OperationAlgorithm
    运算算法接口，是所有算法的抽象，具体实现请您查阅api node

    The operation algorithm interface is the abstraction of all algorithms. For the specific implementation, please refer to the api node

    作者:
    Ling Yu Zhao

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      String getAlgorithmName() 
      boolean init()
      算法模块的初始化方法，在这里您可以进行组件的初始化方法，当初始化成功之后，该算法就可以处于就绪的状态，一般这里就是将自己添加到算法管理类中 The initialization method of the algorithm module, here you can perform the initialization method of the component, when the initialization is successful, the algorithm can be in a ready state, generally here is to add yourself to the algorithm management class

    • 方法详细资料

      • getAlgorithmName

        String getAlgorithmName()
        返回:
        该算法组件的名称，也是一个识别码，在获取算法的时候您可以通过该名称获取到算法对象

        The name of the algorithm component is also an identification code. You can obtain the algorithm object through this name when obtaining the algorithm.

      • init

        boolean init()
        算法模块的初始化方法，在这里您可以进行组件的初始化方法，当初始化成功之后，该算法就可以处于就绪的状态，一般这里就是将自己添加到算法管理类中

        The initialization method of the algorithm module, here you can perform the initialization method of the component, when the initialization is successful, the algorithm can be in a ready state, generally here is to add yourself to the algorithm management class

        返回:
        初始化成功或失败。

        Initialization succeeded or failed.
